nhc_headline: ...NARDA HOLDING STEADY WELL OUT TO SEA...
summary: ...NARDA HOLDING STEADY WELL OUT TO SEA... As of 2:00 PM PDT Fri Sep 26 the center of Narda was located near 17.1, -122.7 with movement WNW at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 979 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 90 mph.
